## VM Args Template for TLS Mode E2E Tests
## Variables: {{NODE_NAME}}, {{DIST_PORT}}, {{SSL_DIST_OPTFILE}}

-sname {{NODE_NAME}}
-setcookie temporary_will_be_exchanged

## Disable standard EPMD
-start_epmd false

## Use TLS EPMD module
-epmd_module gsmlg_epmd_tls

## Distribution port
-erl_epmd_port {{DIST_PORT}}

## TLS distribution protocol
-proto_dist inet_tls
-ssl_dist_optfile {{SSL_DIST_OPTFILE}}

## Kernel configuration
-kernel inet_dist_listen_min {{DIST_PORT}}
-kernel inet_dist_listen_max {{DIST_PORT}}

## Code paths
-pa {{CODE_PATHS}}

## Test-specific settings
+P 1048576
+Q 1048576
